room_title: Escape room "Secret Agent 777" by Tyler Escape Room in Tyler
room_description: Come discover if you have what it takes to go undercover as a Special Operations Agent! Your country needs you to enter the office of an international spy who has activated a bomb in order to destroy valuable information. In order to survive and be successful with your mission, you must uncover the name and location of Agent 777, diffuse the bomb, and find the combination to the internal locking system device which has you captive in his office.
